{"name":"盜賊技能（盜賊）","type":"ability","img":"/systems/ose/assets/default/ability.png","data":{"pattern":"white","requirements":"","roll":"1d100","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false,"description":"<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 16pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Arial; color: #38761d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">盜賊技能</span></h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">盜賊可以使用以下技能，成功的機率顯示在下：</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">▶ 攀登陡峭的表面（CS）：每攀爬 100 英尺就需要進行一次擲骰。如果失敗，盜賊會在半途跌落，承受跌落傷害。</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">▶ 尋找或拆除寶藏陷阱（TR）：需要擲骰子來找到一個藏寶陷阱，然後再擲骰來移除它。每個陷阱只能嘗試一次。</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">▶ 聽取噪音（HN）。在一個安靜的環境中（例如不是在戰鬥中），盜賊可以嘗試在門邊聽，或者聽到一些東西（例如一個遊蕩的怪物）接近的聲音。</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">▶ 躲在陰影中（HS）：要求盜賊不動聲色&mdash;隱藏時不可能進行攻擊或移動。盜賊可以嘗試在不被注意的情況下潛入敵人身邊。</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">▶ 開鎖 (OL)：需要盜賊工具（見裝備，第42頁）。盜賊對每個鎖只能嘗試這個技能一次。在獲得經驗值之前，盜賊不能再次嘗試同一個鎖。</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">▶ 偷竊口袋（PP）：如果受害者超過 5 級，盜賊擲骰每超過 5 級就會受到 5% 的懲罰。總是有至少 1% 的失敗機會。擲出超過成功所需百分比的兩倍意味著偷竊企圖被發現。GM 應確定受害者的反應（可能使用第114頁遭遇戰中的反應表）。</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"border: none; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 321px; height: 413px;\"><img style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/O-ZGfsGanfxkRoLSiX_N_AhEj2SPAwPjK_GJugyWLRMMcJzjRQGGQU3mHSeJD15RbIJ8TDA-dvk0rg4rivF6RGfXAtJZtIYN1O_DoCKcobdMCUDAt7d1_l2OvOw5N-5Xxh943DC3=s0\" width=\"321\" height=\"413\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-63abe617-7fff-6466-ed45-f73193cda24a\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\"></strong></p>","save":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qFNtGpfu1tQ6mtE5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_b0rhr7hpfcc","path":"各種能力","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"JmN2U16ugvQVyAUC"}
